MIZORAM LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY GENERAL ELECTION CHANCHIN TLANGPUI

 

            Mizoram ah Ditrict Council hun lai atang tawh khan Political party hrang hrang ten nasa tak in hruaitu nih hi an lo in chuh thin a  a tlangpuiin party beh chhan nei lo achuh chu tlin a hart hi hle a hmun then khatah chuan tling hi an awm zauh zauh ve bawk thin

 

            District Council hunlai atang a Political party leh Independent a chuh tu te din hmun chu hetiang hi a ni.

 

            Kum 1952 a District council inthlan buatsaih anih khan  Mizoram chu Circle 18 ah then ani in he mi in thlan neih hmasak ber tum hian Mizo Union leh Zalen party ten an chuh a, Mizo Union in seat 16 la in sawrkar na  an siam a, chuta  thlan tlin te chu:

 

            1)      R thanhlira                                   Mizo Union

            2)      Hrangaia                                      Mizo Union

            3)      Lalbuaia                                      Mizo Union

            4)      Lalsawia                                      Mizo Union

            5)      Chaltuahkhuma                            Mizo Union

            6)      P Saitawna                                  Mizo Union

            7)      Hrangkhuma                                Mizo Union

            8)      Rotluanga                                    Mizo Union

            9)      F Sangkunga                               Mizo Union

            10)    RB Chawnga                               Mizo Union

            11)    Papuia                                         Mizo Union

            12)    Pathala                                        Mizo Union

            13)    Ch. Saprawnga                            Mizo Union

            14)    Khuaimawnga                              Mizo Union

            15)    Vakoha                                       Mizo Union

            16)    Tuikhurliana                                 Mizo Union

            17)    Lairopuia                                     Zalen

            18)    Pachhunga                                   Zalen

 

            District Council hunlai  Assam hnuaia  MLA inthlan kan hmachhawn hmasak ber  khan Mizo Union leh Zalen  chuan MLA seat thum kan neih chu an in chuh a, a result chu a hnuai a mi ang hi a ni:

           

            1)   Aizawl East         Ch Saprawnga                 Mizo Union

            2)   Aizawl west         R Thanhlira                      Mizo Union

            3)   Lungleh               R Dengthuama                 Mizo Union

 

           

            District Council inthlan vawihnihna chu  dt 25.1.1957 khan neih ani a Mizo Union, Zalen leh Right Wing ten an chuh a a result chu a hnuai ami ang hi ani

 

            1)      Vanlalbuka                      Mizo Union

            2)      Kaibuaia                          Mizo Union

            3)      Chaltuahkhuma                Mizo Union

            Kum 1957 khan Assam hnuaiah  MLA inthlan vawi hnih na neih leh ani a Mizo Union, Zalen leh Right Wing-ten an chuh a, a result chu a hnuai ami ang hi ani:

 

            1)   Aizawl east             A Thanglura                     Mizo union

            2)   Aizawl West           Lalmawia                         Zalen

            3)   Lungleh                  C Thuamluaia                  Zalen

 

            District Council in thlan vawi thumna dt 5.2.1962  khan neih ani a he in thlanah hian Mizo Union, Zalen, Congress, EITU leh Tribal ten an chuh a, a hnuai ami ang hi a result chu ani:

 

            1)      C Pahlira                         Mizo Union

            2)      HK Bawichhuaka            Mizo Union

            3)      Hrangaia                          Mizo Union

            4)      Kaibuaia                          Mizo Union

            Kum 1962 khan Assam hnuaia MLA in thlan hun ani a, Mizoramah chuan Political Party  pali Mizo Union, Congress, Zalen leh APHLC ten an chuh a, a result chu ahnuai a mi ang hi ani:

 

            1)   Aizawl East            R thanhlira                    APHLC

            2)   Aizawl west            Ch Chunga                   Mizo Union

            3)   Lungleh                  Ch Saprawnga              APHLC

 

            Kum 1962 a thlan tlin  Ch Saprawnga leh Ch Chunga te chu Conference thu ang a an ban tak avangin  dt 23 4 1963 khan Bye election neih ani a Aizawl west Bial ah          J. Manliana  MNF leh Lungleh Bial ah LH Mawia te thlan tlin an ni.

 

            Kum 1966 kum khan Mizoram alo buai ta a  Kum 1967 ah MLA thlan a lo hun leh a  Aizawl East leh West ah A, Thangluran a chuh a  chuh tu awmlo a thlan tlin ani a Lungleh ah pawh chuh tu awm lo in Lalchhunga than tlin ani bawk, Aizawl West            A Thanglura chhuahsan ah J Manliana thlan tlin ani leh bawk ani.

            He election-ah hian MNF party chuan MLA seat 22 changin sawrkarna an siam a, independent candidate PP Thawlan a thlawp bakah Pu Zoramthanga bial chhuahsan Kolasib Bye-Election-ah MNF Candidate K. Amaherawhchu he election-ah hian kum danga la awm ngailo Suangpuilawn bialah Pu Lalsangzuala, Independent Candidate chu HPC (D) ten Campaign puiin vauna nen VC leh khawtlang hruaitute hnenah silai mu te semin Pu Lalsangzuala vote tling ngei turin an hriattir leh party dang candidate te kidnapped a awm avangin sawiselna a nasa hle. Central YMA pawhin MLA thlantlin Lalsangzuala chu an ensan hial a ni.

MIZORAM LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY GENERAL ELECTION CHANCHIN TLANGPUI

 

            Mizoram ah Ditrict Council hun lai atang tawh khan Political party hrang hrang ten nasa tak in hruaitu nih hi an lo in chuh thin a  a tlangpuiin party beh chhan nei lo achuh chu tlin a hart hi hle a hmun then khatah chuan tling hi an awm zauh zauh ve bawk thin

 

            District Council hunlai atang a Political party leh Independent a chuh tu te din hmun chu hetiang hi a ni.

 

            Kum 1952 a District council inthlan buatsaih anih khan  Mizoram chu Circle 18 ah then ani in he mi in thlan neih hmasak ber tum hian Mizo Union leh Zalen party ten an chuh a, Mizo Union in seat 16 la in sawrkar na  an siam a, chuta  thlan tlin te chu:

 

            1)      R thanhlira                                   Mizo Union

            2)      Hrangaia                                      Mizo Union

            3)      Lalbuaia                                      Mizo Union

            4)      Lalsawia                                      Mizo Union

            5)      Chaltuahkhuma                            Mizo Union

            6)      P Saitawna                                  Mizo Union

            7)      Hrangkhuma                                Mizo Union

            8)      Rotluanga                                    Mizo Union

            9)      F Sangkunga                               Mizo Union

            10)    RB Chawnga                               Mizo Union

            11)    Papuia                                         Mizo Union

            12)    Pathala                                        Mizo Union

            13)    Ch. Saprawnga                            Mizo Union

            14)    Khuaimawnga                              Mizo Union

            15)    Vakoha                                       Mizo Union

            16)    Tuikhurliana                                 Mizo Union

            17)    Lairopuia                                     Zalen

            18)    Pachhunga                                   Zalen

 

            District Council hunlai  Assam hnuaia  MLA inthlan kan hmachhawn hmasak ber  khan Mizo Union leh Zalen  chuan MLA seat thum kan neih chu an in chuh a, a result chu a hnuai a mi ang hi a ni:

           

            1)   Aizawl East         Ch Saprawnga                 Mizo Union

            2)   Aizawl west         R Thanhlira                      Mizo Union

            3)   Lungleh               R Dengthuama                 Mizo Union
